'''Bemberg''' or '''Bemberg silk''' is the [[trade name]] for a special kind of [[rayon]]. It is frequently used for lining high quality [[suit]]s and [[coat]]s. Bemberg silk is a cheaper and more versatile substitute for natural [[silk]].{{citation needed}}

